com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.dialogcomponents.swing

Class NestedDropdownTextField.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.dialogcomponents.swing.NestedDropdownTextField.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    NestedDropdownTextField

    public static class NestedDropdownTextField.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    A Builder class to create a NestedDropdownTextField. The Builder can only be used once. Once used, by a call to build(), subsequent calls of build() will throw UnsupportedOperationException, as will attempts to add additional menu items
    Since:
    1.28.0
    Author:
    S.Roughley knime@vernalis.com
